&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Exciting Opportunity for Advanced Practitioners &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Doncaster Urgent and Emergency Care&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Salary: Aligned to AFC Band 8a (Full/Part time)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;FCMS has recently been awarded a new contract to deliver Integrated and Emergency care across the Doncaster locality. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Our advanced practitioners work across all disciplines developing and enhancing the clinical services for patients across Doncaster Urgent and Emergency Care. We work together to ensure our patients get the right advice at the right time in the right place. FCMS works really hard, we love what we do and are seriously focused on our patients and staff. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;You must have extensive and substantial clinical experience within an unscheduled care setting, working at advanced practitioner level in an ever evolving environment. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Services include&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Doncaster Urgent Treatment Centre&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mexborough Urgent Treatment Centre&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Doncaster Same Day Health Centre&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Acute Visiting Service&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Being competent and confident in every aspect of your work, alongside living and breathing our behaviours and values is really important to us. We are a dynamic business, committed to sustaining our organisational longevity and doing the very best for the people we serve.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Company Values – &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;*&lt;strong&gt;FUN&lt;/strong&gt;**&lt;strong&gt;AWESOME&lt;/strong&gt;**&lt;strong&gt;BRAVE&lt;/strong&gt;**&lt;strong&gt;GO-GETTING&lt;/strong&gt;**&lt;strong&gt;OOMPF&lt;/strong&gt;**&lt;strong&gt;HUMBLE&lt;/strong&gt;*&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Interested? We hope so! For more information please contact: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;fcms.hr@nhs.net&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
